Package info.kgeorgiy.ja.gerasimov.implementor

Class Implementor

  • java.lang.Object
    • info.kgeorgiy.ja.gerasimov.implementor.Implementor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Impler, JarImpler
    public class Implementor
extends Object
implements JarImpler
    The Implementor class. This class generate implementations of classes or interfaces. Command-line argument: The full name of the class / interface to generate the implementation. As a result, the java code of the class with the "Impl" suffix be generated, extending (implementing) the specified class (interface).
    • Generated class classes name be same as classes name of the type token with Impl suffix added.
    • The generated class compile without errors.
    • The generated class not abstract.
    • Methods of the generated class ignore their arguments and return default values.
